#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resource.rst:129
msgid ""
"Duplicates the resource, returning a new resource. By default, sub-"
"resources are shared between resource copies for efficiency, this can be "
"changed by passing ``true`` to the ``subresources`` argument."
msgstr ""
"复制资源，返回一个新资源。默认情况下，子资源在资源副本之间，共享以提高效率，这可以通过将 ``true`` 传递给 "
"``subresources`` 参数来更改。"

