msgid ":ref:`RID <class_RID>` **get_rid** **(** **)** const"
msgstr ":ref:`RID <class_RID>` **get_rid** **(** **)** const"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resource.rst:145
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Returns the RID of the resource (or an empty RID). Many resources (such "
"as :ref:`Texture2D <class_Texture2D>`, :ref:`Mesh <class_Mesh>`, etc) are"
" high-level abstractions of resources stored in a server, so this "
"function will return the original RID."
msgstr ""
"返回资源的RID（或一个空RID）。许多资源（例如 :ref:`Texture <class_Texture>`、:ref:`Mesh "
"<class_Mesh>` 等）是服务器中存储的资源的高级抽象，因此此函数将返回原始RID。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resource.rst:151
msgid "void **setup_local_to_scene** **(** **)**"
msgstr "void **setup_local_to_scene** **(** **)**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resource.rst:153
msgid ""
"This method is called when a resource with :ref:`resource_local_to_scene "
"<class_Resource_property_resource_local_to_scene>` enabled is loaded from"
" a :ref:`PackedScene <class_PackedScene>` instantiation. Its behavior can"
" be customized by overriding :ref:`_setup_local_to_scene "
"<class_Resource_method__setup_local_to_scene>` from script."
msgstr ""
"当一个带有启用 :ref:`resource_local_to_scene "
"<class_Resource_property_resource_local_to_scene>` 的资源，从一个 "
":ref:`PackedScene <class_PackedScene>` 实例化加载时，该方法被调用。可以通过覆盖脚本中的 "
":ref:`_setup_local_to_scene "
"<class_Resource_method__setup_local_to_scene>`，来自定义其行为。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resource.rst:155
msgid ""
"For most resources, this method performs no base logic. "
":ref:`ViewportTexture <class_ViewportTexture>` performs custom logic to "
"properly set the proxy texture and flags in the local viewport."
msgstr ""
"对于大多数资源，此方法不执行任何基本逻辑。:ref:`ViewportTexture <class_ViewportTexture>` "
"执行自定义逻辑，以在本地视图中，正确设置代理纹理和标志。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resource.rst:161
msgid "void **take_over_path** **(** :ref:`String <class_String>` path **)**"
msgstr "void **take_over_path** **(** :ref:`String <class_String>` path **)**"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resource.rst:163
msgid ""
"Sets the path of the resource, potentially overriding an existing cache "
"entry for this path. This differs from setting :ref:`resource_path "
"<class_Resource_property_resource_path>`, as the latter would error out "
"if another resource was already cached for the given path."
msgstr ""
"设置资源的路径，可能会覆盖该路径的现有缓存条目。这不同于设置 :ref:`resource_path "
"<class_Resource_property_resource_path>`，因为如果已经为给定路径缓存了另一个资源，后者将出错。"

